"gleaming the cube"

02:08.362 --> 02:09.294
doesn't mean anything,
right?

02:09.296 --> 02:12.331
Well, neither does
half the crap I say.

02:12.432 --> 02:15.267
Oz! Oz! we've got
an emergency.

02:15.269 --> 02:16.435
I just got a call
from Corporate!

02:16.437 --> 02:18.103
Heather O'Brien is gonna
be here any minute.

02:18.105 --> 02:21.440
