I don't know,

02:22.610 --> 02:25.844
but I do know that if this place
doesn't look like a million bucks,

02:25.846 --> 02:27.980
she is gonna have my head
on a platter.

02:27.982 --> 02:32.017
We need pops of color,
brighter lights, more attractive people!

02:32.019 --> 02:32.751
What?
Uh...

02:32.753 --> 02:35.387
