big, green marble.

02:58.311 --> 03:00.479
Hi. I'm looking for Oz.

03:00.481 --> 03:01.880
You and three
deposed dictators.

03:01.882 --> 03:04.950
I am he.
Welcome to Master Control.

03:04.952 --> 03:06.118
