Wow.

03:06.120 --> 03:07.452
I'd heard you were
a man of mystery,

03:07.454 --> 03:10.722
but, uh, they didn't tell me
how handsome you were.

03:11.057 --> 03:11.924
Careful, Oz.

03:11.926 --> 03:13.926
Remember what Vee said.
Yeah.

03:13.928 --> 03:15.460
Dinobots. Cool.

03:15.462 --> 03:17.296
A lot of people think
that's where  <i>Transformers</i>

03:17.298 --> 03:19.264
