for you putting up with us.

03:29.310 --> 03:30.709
How nice.

03:31.512 --> 03:33.478
A 2009 Donn Shaw?

03:33.480 --> 03:35.280
That's my favorite
Riesling.

03:35.282 --> 03:35.847
Oh.

03:35.849 --> 03:38.483
Check it out.

03:38.485 --> 03:39.351
Psst!

03:39.353 --> 03:42.854
Cawk-Oz! Cawk-Oz! Cawk-Oz!

03:42.856 --> 03:45.257
