to keep an air of mystery.

04:38.245 --> 04:39.911
Ah, and I respect
that point, Oz,

04:39.913 --> 04:43.448
but judging by your web page,
a little too mysterious.

04:44.952 --> 04:46.418
Yeah, I Googled "Contra,"
and all that comes up

04:46.420 --> 04:50.622
is some Nintendo game
that's, like, older than me.

04:50.923 --> 04:52.491
